        "id": 1811081829,
        "number": 129,
        "title": "processEngine的reload方法，无法重新加载.bpmn的内容",
        "state": "closed",
        "created_at": "2023-07-19T03:35:03Z",
        "updated_at": "2024-10-29T10:09:26Z",
        "closed_at": "2023-08-04T10:10:34Z",
        "author": "CiicDong",
        "comments": 2,
        "labels": [],
        "assignees": [],
        "locked": false,
        "body": "```java  public void reLoad() {\r\n        final String code = \"bpmn.ktvExample1\";\r\n        processEngine.preCompile(code);\r\n        processEngine.reload(code);\r\n        System.out.println(processEngine.getJavaCode(code));\r\n    }\r\n\r\n上面的代码当我修改了`ktvExample.bpmn20`文件里的sign方法，修改为sign1。之后重新进行reload，或者是编译之后reload，都无法运行新的sign1方法",
        "url": "https://github.com/alibaba/compileflow/issues/129"
    },
